cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.CV 

This paper deals with reinforcement learning and control of physical robots, which falls under the robotics (cs.RO) sub-category. The use of a Kalman filter for model fitting and exploration also involves machine learning (cs.LG) and control systems (cs.SY). The paper also mentions the use of model-free reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper involves contact manipulation, which can be related to computer vision (cs.CV) for perception and recognition of objects.
